{"tid":1296268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國黃背心示威者，在每個星期六湧上街頭","createTime":"2019-07-08T10:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:36:24.000Z","uid":73092,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e06db4d46a088ae942cafa359e34836fbbcb2fa4","tid":1296268,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpTBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=52b1f27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭</span></span>，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"},{"pid":"6c6ade31d290e5485324f35665108d185e8c67c1","tid":1296268,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d48553e844310346cc93437529a33e03f2cf8d9","tid":1296268,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36db9e5a9e6ec0bb5046c8a38ebec126ac369a3a","tid":1296268,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40799188699241268f6a8db068130819da3b8c9e","tid":1296268,"uid":73092,"like":0,"disli